document_notes.text:
This update for libqt5-qtbase fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2020-17507: Fixed a buffer overflow in XBM parser (bsc#1176315)
- Made handling of XDG_RUNTIME_DIR more secure (bsc#1172515)

notes.text: An issue was discovered in Qt through 5.12.9, and 5.13.x through 5.15.x before 5.15.1. read_xbm_body in gui/image/qxbmhandler.cpp has a buffer over-read.
